'''Tsen-zi-wun''' (千字文) geh yen miang heh "Tsi wan [[Wong Hi-zi]] si tsen zi". Gaai si heung Naam-tsiu-leung (502 nen-549 nen) zok-saa. 

[[Saam-zi-gang]], [[Baak-gaa-seng]] tung Tsen-zi-wun hap tsang "Saam baak tsen". Heung yu Hon-zi wun-fa geh gok-gaa haau  chung-yew.
